    p Hyde Park Ice Pavilion was built in 1970 and recently has completed a 9 million dollar renovation. This included all locker rooms, ices surfaces, boards, bleaches, lobby, bar, and lounge.
    p With two brand new ice pads, J.R. Stoneroom bar and Lounge, Hyde Park Ice Pavilion has become a premiere rink in Western New York.

