    h3 Come Join All The Fun At Hyde Park Ice Pavilion
    p Hyde Park is the Proud Home of the Niagara Ice Hawks, Hills Hockey Development, Niagara Falls and Grand Island hockey. In additions we have skaters of all different ages from our learn to skate programs all the way to our “senior” leagues. We also offer public skating Fridays through Sundays!
